data.description: Exquisite modernized Plano home in a prime location! 2023 kitchen updates boast quartz counters, backsplash, white cabinetry, and SS appliances. Open living and dining are adorned with crown molding, and drenched in welcoming natural light. Chic wood-look laminate flooring spans common areas. Contemporary paint palette throughout. The private primary suite features a bay window, dual vanities, a walk-in shower, and a garden tub. New bedroom carpets, AC units, ductwork, blinds, and faucets. The roof was replaced in 2021. Your sophisticated haven awaits!
